Class BasicVarString

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.constraints.impl.CommonBase
      • javax.constraints.impl.AbstractConstrainedVariable
        • javax.constraints.impl.BasicVarString
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConstrainedVariable, VarString

    public class BasicVarString
extends AbstractConstrainedVariable
implements VarString
    BasicVarString are a special type of constrained variables that are defined using an array of string values.
